@NODE INFORMATION "INFORMATION"

@{b}VERSION@{ub}:

MidiPlay v2.65b 10-Apr-96

If you need the latest version of MidiPlay, look at my WWW Amiga page:
http://www.uta.fi/~csjasy/amiga.html

Unfortunately there is currently no support BBS.

@{b}REQUIREMENTS@{ub}

	MidiPlay   requires   at  least  OS  2.04  to  run.   Also
	midi.library  and  miditune.library  are required.  If you
	want  to  really  hear  something,  you need external MIDI
	equipments and a MIDI file.

