	 both CC 0 and CC 32 messages.

v2.25	22-Nov-94

	 Window positions with open/closed and zoom information can
	 be saved to an environment file.  This file will be loaded
	 automatically when started.  Next number in the buffer can
	 be seen in the main window's screen title.

	23-Nov-94

	 Added   NOTEON   and  NOTEOFF  commands.   Added  PORTNAME
