	 Added  REFRESHLYRICS and AUTOLYRICS  commands. SENDMIDIDATA
	 available in tooltype format.

v2.64b	1-Dec-95

	 Fixed lyric refresh  bug when  autolyrics used  first time.
	 SYSEX command available in tooltype format.

v2.64c	27-Jan-96

	 Fixed tempo bug:  tempo change wasn't set on if a song had
	 a tempo tooltype and it was selected by pressing a gadget.
	 Small  addition to tempo command.  Added short delay after
	 a normally ended song.

v2.65	3-Apr-96

	 Buffer  has  no  limit anymore.  RANDOMBUFFER command puts
	 playlist entries randomly into the buffer.

v2.65b	10-Apr-96

	 Moved    delay    after    song    to   miditune.library's
	 responsibility.   Menus and some gadgets set independently
	 from the type of event.

@ENDNODE

